We might as well do this right.  There are four options:

You can have -forwarder=X (n times), 
--no-forwarders, 
--auto-forwarders, and 
--auto-forwarders --forwarder=X (n times)

To do this, we want something like:

(% if enable_dns_forwarding -%}
{% for dns in dns_forwarder_address %}
    --forwarder={{ dns }} \
{% endfor %}
{% if enable_auto_forward is true -%}
    --auto-forwarders \
{% endif %}
{% else %}
   -- no-forwarders
{% endif %}

